room_title: Escape room "Red Carpet" by MindBreak in St. Louis
review: We went as a group of friends for birthdays. We really enjoyed it! We made it out alive!!!! We will definitely go back.

room_title: Escape room "Red Carpet" by MindBreak in St. Louis
review: This was our first escape room so we were not sure what to expect. We had so much fun! There were 6 of us and we barely escaped! The workers were gracious to us and gave us an extra clue or two! Will definitely return if we are in the area!
